# Feature: filter
# Scenario Outline: color Filtering
# Given online customer is on the e-commerce website product listing page.
# When an online customer selects the option to filter the list of products by a given "<color>".
# Then only those products in the list are shown that have the given "<color>"
# Examples:
#     | color |
#     | red  |

# Scenario Outline: Size Filtering
# Given online customer is on the e-commerce website product listing page.
# When an online customer selects the option to filter the list of products by a given size "<Size>".
# Then only those products in the list are shown that have the given size "<Size>"
# Examples:
#     | Size |
#     | XL  |